        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[2024LPL 春季赛：UP 2-0 RA，UP 连下两城完成惊天翻盘]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>2024 英雄联盟 LPL 春季赛 UP vs RA，UP 2-0 RA，UP 连下两城完成惊天翻盘。</p><p><img data-width="1178" data-height="723" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/B9/rBUBsmXfAEWAcyNjAAGiqYKPQ-E034.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>第一局 BP</strong></p><p><img data-width="1352" data-height="746" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E2/rBUC6GXfAGaAR1GjAANHH3UklPM975.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>赛况</strong></p><p>第 1 分钟，RA 一级埋伏成功，naiyou 击杀 H4cker 拿下一血。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E2/rBUC6GXfANuAXM2kAGk3aekSXJ4132.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 11 分钟，RA 拿下小龙，后续团战 UP 击杀 naiyou。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E3/rBUC6GXfA5aAH4y-AKUvX-tQLHs906.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 22 分钟，双方河道团战，UP 打出 1 换 3 随后拿下小龙。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E3/rBUC6GXfA4uAH5IGALIc1ju5Yy0142.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 24 分钟，RA 野辅阵亡，UP 拿下大龙。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E3/rBUC6GXfA6eAQYreAKpTjG7l4s8947.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 31 分钟，UP 中路推进，Yuekai 收获三杀，UP 一波 0 换 4 结束比赛。</p><p><strong>赛后数据</strong></p><p><img data-width="1298" data-height="709" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BA/rBUBsmXfA7qAQeE6AAJlEg1lAWI080.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1289" data-height="706" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BA/rBUBsmXfA8aAIwuzAAKWxLgZE5w554.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1288" data-height="698" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BB/rBUBsmXfA9yAMqdyAAJaVnTK_ho036.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>第二局 BP</strong></p><p><img data-width="1356" data-height="755" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E5/rBUC6GXfCPSAFx9zAAQMh_ShjF0908.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><strong>赛况</strong></p><p>第 16 分钟，双方围绕听牌龙爆发团战，Assum 拿下一血，RA 打出 1 换 3，UP 拿下听牌龙，但 UP 中二塔被推。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E7/rBUC6GXfDYKAdVWVAMtOmYSYJ30413.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 21 分钟，上路混战，RA 打出 1 换 3 拿下大龙，UP 偷下电龙魂。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BF/rBUBsmXfDj2ABpx2AMvEiUCYYqY075.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 26 分钟，贾克斯中路绕后 TP 配合大树大招先手开团，Yuekai 背靠太阳圆盘换掉两个，RA 打出 3 换 5。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BF/rBUBsmXfEA-ARgJUALn381NsH74710.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 27 分钟，H4cker 抢下远古龙击杀 Xiaoxu 随后再拿下大龙。</p><p>第 33 分钟，远古龙团，Assum 落单，UP 打出 1 换 3 拿下远古龙。</p><p><img src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/BF/rBUBsmXfEAWAInCFAMj8V4v9HSc425.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>第 37 分钟，UP 三龙汇推进，高地 1 换 4 一波推平基地。</p><p><strong>赛后数据</strong></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="388" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/C0/rBUBsmXfENeAGqi-AAD5QxZXH48844.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="388" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E8/rBUC6GXfEN-AcPm4AAEcYKdu9Vg553.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="388" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/C0/rBUBsmXfEOSAfGTkAAEf4GWUk-M436.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
            </description>
