                <![CDATA[<p>北京时间 2 月 28 日，中国 CS 战队 LVG 在 Major 亚洲 RMR 中让一追二战胜 Grayhound，成功跻身 PGL 哥本哈根 Major！</p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="1147" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E7/rBUC6GXfDYmAUmqYAAPD1kt1IKc758.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>在亚洲区 MajorRMR 败者组决赛中，LVG2-1 战胜 Grahound，完成让一追二成功晋级 PGL 哥本哈根 Major，结束了 CNCS 连续三届（855 天）无缘 Major 正赛的尴尬纪录。</p><p><img data-width="801" data-height="562" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/C0/rBUBsmXfEP6AR3QoAAE4RCTsvKQ470.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="tips_i">三张图总数据</span></p><p>图一 Vertigo 6-13</p><p><img data-width="804" data-height="556" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E8/rBUC6GXfET2AHszJAAE7MxyaQ5k334.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="tips_i">图一数据</span></p><p>图二 Anubis 13-7</p><p><img data-width="805" data-height="560" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E8/rBUC6GXfEWmAbmKFAAE561t4EvM200.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="tips_i">图二数据</span></p><p>图三 Nuke 13-2</p><p><img data-width="802" data-height="556" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/48/C0/rBUBsmXfEXqAXDBAAAEzDrWJfxg954.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="tips_i">图三数据</span></p><p><img data-width="690" data-height="414" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4C/E7/rBUC6GXfDheABI1pAAD4Igl-YfE108.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
